            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character can\u2019t resist a second (or fifth) helping of roast boar or honeyed bread, leaving them perpetually stuffed and sluggish. Their belt groans under the strain of their indulgences and dodging a farmer\u2019s angry goose is a sweaty ordeal. Festivals are their downfall, as they waddle away from the feast table. Graceful movement is a distant dream.",
